"15  black peppercorns","7  thyme sprigs","1  head garlic, halved horizontally","1  bay leaf","8 cups water","4 cups fresh field peas (white acre, lady peas, or black-eyed peas), rinsed","2 teaspoons kosher salt, divided","1/2 cup minced celery","1/2 cup minced red onion","1/2 cup coarsely chopped fresh flat-leaf parsley","1/3 cup extra-virgin olive oil","1/4 cup Banyuls vinegar or Champagne or white wine vinegar","1 tablespoon Dijon mustard","3/8 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper"